msgstr "void kile.wizard.tabular();"

#. Tag: para
#: scripting.docbook:1399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Calls the <emphasis>Tabular wizard</emphasis>, which helps to write a "
"tabular environment (see <xref linkend=\"wizard_array\" role=\"select: title "
